WEBVTT

00:08:58.375 --> 00:09:00.518
that makes us not care.

00:09:00.542 --> 00:09:02.143
So we have policies

00:09:02.167 --> 00:09:04.768
that are returning people back to Mexico,

00:09:04.792 --> 00:09:06.143
so they can wait.

00:09:06.167 --> 00:09:08.167
And they wait there for months.

00:09:09.167 --> 00:09:11.226
In conditions that are horrible,

00:09:11.250 --> 00:09:13.292
where people are suffering and hurting.

00:09:14.417 --> 00:09:15.809
Abuses.

00:09:15.833 --> 00:09:19.125
And not even the means to be OK.

00:09:20.542 --> 00:09:23.458
I think that it is true

00:09:24.792 --> 00:09:27.542
that we must keep our country safe,

00:09:28.667 --> 00:09:32.351
that we must make sure
who enters our country,